data.description: *PAID-OFF Solar* Welcome to your dream home in the highly sought-after San Diego Country Estates. This spacious condo, spanning 1,847 square feet, offers a luxurious living experience in a desirable complex. The property features three oversized bedrooms, each with its own attached FULL bathroom, with the added convenience of a full bedroom and bathroom located on the bottom story. Step into the heart of the home, where the kitchen stands out with its modern updates. Enjoy the beauty of stunning quartz countertops, ample cabinet storage, and efficient appliances. Natural light fills the space through large windows and the vaulted ceiling creating a bright and welcoming atmosphere complemented by newer hard flooring that extends throughout the entire home.  Parking is a breeze with a carport and a one-car garage, which also provides additional storage in the patio shed. The private fenced back patio opens up to breathtaking views of the San Vicente golf course, offering an idyllic setting for enjoying stunning sunrises and sunsets. Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry facilities and stay comfortable year-round with central air conditioning and heating, controlled by a wall or app-controlled thermostat. The property has been updated with a modern electrical panel for added peace of mind. Within the complex, residents can take advantage of community amenities such as a pool and jacuzzi. Additionally, the San Diego Country Estates offers an array of perks, including tennis courts, basketball courts, horse riding traiWithin the complex, residents can take advantage of community amenities such as a pool and jacuzzi. Additionally, the San Diego Country Estates offers an array of perks, including tennis courts, basketball courts, horse riding trails and facilities, playgrounds, a dog park, golf course access, hiking trails, and more. This home, well-loved and meticulously maintained, is truly move-in ready. Seize the opportunity to experience luxury living in one of San Diego's most desirable communities. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and make this stunning condo your new home.
